## **Triadic Delta Engine (SID / PED / Q□ / TRIAD)**  
Explicit about the relational semantics.

```
def apply_triadic_deltas(E, modes):

    D = init_delta_tensor_like(E)

    for z in range(E.Z):
        for y in range(E.Y):
            for x in range(E.X):

                # SID delta (structural)
                if x > 0:
                    D.sid[z][y][x] = E[z][y][x] - E[z][y][x-1]

                # PED delta (flux)
                if y > 0:
                    D.ped[z][y][x] = E[z][y][x] - E[z][y-1][x]

                # Q□ delta (closure iteration)
                if z > 0:
                    D.qbox[z][y][x] = E[z][y][x] - E[z-1][y][x]

                # TRIAD delta (invariant difference)
                inv_curr = invariant(E[z][y][x])
                inv_prev = invariant(E[z-1][y-1][x-1]) if (z>0 and y>0 and x>0) else 0
                D.triad[z][y][x] = inv_curr - inv_prev

    return D
```

